      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，方向用LR从左到右展开。Exception放在最左边作为基类。HttpException继承自它，然后BadRequestException、UnauthorizedException这些都挂在HttpException下面，对吗？",
